flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[User opens Watch-App]
    B --> C{Is Smartwatch connected?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Display main interface]
    C -->|No| E[Prompt user to connect Smartwatch]
    E --> F[User connects Smartwatch]
    F --> D
    D --> G[User selects feature]
    G --> H{Feature type}
    H -->|Health| I[Display health metrics]
    H -->|Notifications| J[Show notifications]
    H -->|Settings| K[Open settings menu]
    I --> L[User reviews metrics]
    J --> L
    K --> L
    L --> M[User exits feature]
    M --> D
    D --> N[User closes Watch-App]
    N --> O[End]